  "content": {
    "prompt": "<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"passage\"><div class=\"prose style:1\">\n<p class=\"passage_para\">Huntington’s disease has been traced to the number of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"C A G\"><math alttext=\"C A G\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>CAG</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>&nbsp;repeats in the <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"H T T\"><math alttext=\"H T T\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>H</mi><mi>T</mi><mi>T</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>&nbsp;gene, which is located on chromosome 4. The phenotypic influence of individual alleles with different numbers of repeats is shown in Table&nbsp;1.</p>\n<div class=\"table_wrapper\">\n<div class=\"title\"><p class=\"title_line passage-title\">Table 1: Effect of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"C A G\"><math alttext=\"C A G\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>CAG</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> repeat number on Huntington’s disease expression</p></div>\n<table class=\"tgroup cols:2\"><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colname:col1\">\n<span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"C A G\"><math alttext=\"C A G\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>CAG</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> Repeats   </td>\n<td class=\"entry colname:col2\">Expression   </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colname:col1\">\n<span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"less than 27\"><math alttext=\"less than 27\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>27</mn></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> </td>\n<td class=\"entry colname:col2\">No symptoms   </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colname:col1\">27–35   </td>\n<td class=\"entry colname:col2\">No symptoms but increased risk for offspring   </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colname:col1\">36–39   </td>\n<td class=\"entry colname:col2\">May develop symptoms in old age   </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colname:col1\">\n<span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"greater than 40\"><math alttext=\"greater than 40\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>40</mn></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> </td>\n<td class=\"entry colname:col2\">Will express symptoms from an early age   </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n</div>\n</div></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Which of the following is most likely the immediate cause of the first appearance of Huntington’s disease in a person?</p>\n",
    "answer": "i3",
    "choices": [
      {
